This ER diagram illustrates the complete database schema for the TMS Odoo Monolith system. It shows the central transactional entity 'tms_trip' and its relationships with master data such as 'res.partner' (Customers), 'hr.employee' (Drivers), and 'tms_vehicle'. The diagram also includes supporting entities for expenses, proof of delivery, vehicle documents, and auditing. Odoo's extended base models are shown with their original names in parentheses. Some entities like 'tms_route' and 'tms_geofence' are master data tables without direct foreign key links shown in this view.